Enum PropertyValueType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<PropertyValueType>

    public enum PropertyValueType
extends Enum<PropertyValueType>
    Indicates the type of a PropertyValue, and provides a type-safe way to cast it.

    3.0
